Package: scoretable
Title: Score Annotation and Visualization
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul", "Cantalupo", , "pcantalupo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for annotating row observations in a matrix based on
 their highest scoring column and for exploring score distributions across
 predicted labels. While designed for biological applications such as cell
 type annotation, it is fully general and can be applied to any domain with
 a matrix of observations by category scores.
